5 Day Workweek / Office Hours
Good working environment and culture
Attractive benefits and bonuses
Stable working environment | Good career progression

Responsibilites:

  Conduct products/solutions/services presentation
  Engage and build relationships with customers, develop customers’ profiles
  Lead/Manage the tendering/bids process to submission with other functional teams
  Liaise with customers in matters relating to projects, payment, renewal and events/training
  Work with relevant internal/external teams to address customers’ requests and identify customers’ priorities
  Identify, develop and track opportunities to closure; Coordinate proposals from presales and provide quotations to customers

Requirements:

  Supports and contributes to business opportunities
  Develop deep accounts understanding and drive sales closure
  Project organisation skills and good communication &amp; written skills
  Flexible and self-motivated to take on any accounts for development
  Self-directed to plan sales activities and account planning with customers
  At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position
  Self-driven with Technical ICT Solutions sales experience, preferably in SI/reseller environment
  Ability to conduct effective customers’ conversations; understand customers’ requirements with clear documentation skills and coordinate resources internally to support customers’ requests

